# File:             iocp.py
# Description:      IOC Parser is a tool to extract indicators of compromise from security reports
#                   in PDF format.
# Usage:            iocp.py [-h] [-p INI] [-f FORMAT] PDF
# Author:           Armin Buescher (@armbues)
